{"word":"ἠῶθεν","slug":"ἠῶθεν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἠῶθεν</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἠώς'><el>ἠώς</el></a>\n<p/><i>from morn</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>at dawn, at break of day</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <i>this morning</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>like <a href='S:ἕωθεν'><el>ἕωθεν</el></a>\n"}]}